* W02_seq_fail_propagate.sno - sequential pattern: right side fails, whole seq fails
* Rung W02. 'foo' 'xyz' should NOT match 'foobar'.

        subject = 'foobar'
        pat = 'foo' 'xyz'
        subject pat              :s(e001)
        OUTPUT = 'PASS W02/003: seq rightly failed'          :(END)
e001    OUTPUT = 'FAIL W02/003: seq should have failed'
END
